> Don't see a reason to avoid something more complete like what I suggested

I'd like to keep this PR focused on readable thread names with the smallest diff.
Unlike Knots, we still only have `BASIC`, so the small switch makes the thread-name mapping filter-type-specific without reshaping the existing `g_filter_types` code for a possible future filter type.

> could we at least return string_view to avoid premature heap activity

